        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A glass orb atop this metal staff contains fine, undulating sand. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify transmutation magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sigil]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fleet Step]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Jump]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enlarge]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Humanoid Form]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Feet to Fins]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Jump]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vapor Form]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shape Stone]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Humanoid Form]</em></li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cursed Metamorphosis]{Baleful Polymorph}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dragon Form]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Petrify]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
